{"tid":870011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手持bno然後叫人有事走先嗰班人羞唔羞恥？","createTime":"2018-10-20T17:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T03:36:07.000Z","uid":143499,"like":26,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4f6c33451d63b55f001136841d22c32e9f8570","tid":870011,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"當年97主權移交前，成班四五六十歲老屎忽爭崩頭移民去外國避共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發現共產黨唔會行社會主義就仆崩頭咁返嚟爭取北上做生意攞著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家就見到班70後80後叫人爭取bno居英權， 都算啦呢個係你哋97前出世嘅基本人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母雖然帶頭叫人有事BNO走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大敵當前唔團結香港對付中共，個個爭撚住著草，同班冇骨氣嘅中東難民一樣自己家鄉受難，寧願去先進地方做契弟都唔願意為自己嘅民族同尊嚴作任何犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家唔係叫你去死，亦唔係叫你帶頭衝，不過至少唔好帶頭叫人撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總括而言香港人嘅獅子山精神真係冇講錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">縮骨- 有事走先，冇事領功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n算爆- 著數攞到盡，生意賺到盡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老撚土- 話就話國際金融中心，實質民智未開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做人做狗自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"105858dde6ea418f20bb7ae64119261fc3caeff6","tid":870011,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:29:08.000Z","msg":"btw話我五毛嗰啲唔該起底"},{"pid":"4d85d41484872538650746980803b0e4300bd901","tid":870011,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n竟然打錯做雖然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87594e77cfe1123b3a7c3a064975db1af4470fb","tid":870011,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12d9f291296c3621242864da8e57b246e47fdca9","tid":870011,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c87594e77cfe1123b3a7c3a064975db1af4470fb","tid":870011,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:32:58.000Z","msg":"reading 攞U?"},{"pid":"db92b29ef3a6500f7828ae6eda2e3cfc1aae79b3","tid":870011,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d05ee0f52c303bcc195628fae8efe814955ffa0","tid":870011,"uid":41245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:47:34.000Z","msg":"依家連走唔到嘅bno都變咗帶頭走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5e67af51c6b3253bc37f077a0e1f7233393c5e","tid":870011,"uid":161190,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"中國人陋性 正常不過"},{"pid":"e1d5ccbf8c30f8912c3cb135ebefb202a4d77e3b","tid":870011,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d05ee0f52c303bcc195628fae8efe814955ffa0","tid":870011,"uid":41245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:47:34.000Z","msg":"依家連走唔到嘅bno都變咗帶頭走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T00:37:24.000Z","msg":"而家就見到班70後80後叫人爭取bno居英權， 都算啦呢個係你哋97前出世嘅基本人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57bf8d35b480ec88052cd0fba3121e199e2eaf3","tid":870011,"uid":27642,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"講到尾都係因為你乜柒都冇<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\n問心，你有bno/bc 你走唔走？<br />\n<br />\n巴打叫人攞bno，都係想留條後路啫<br />\n同抗爭冇衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520414a5c9